Project context
This is a personal portfolio site for Sam Havas — senior product designer & builder. The site's central concept is Concept 03 "The Build Log": a split-pane hero where the left side is polished editorial copy and the right side is a live GitHub activity feed (samhavasdesign). The portfolio IS the proof of concept — every design and code decision should be intentional and defensible.
Stack
Next.js, React, Tailwind (core utilities only), deployed on Vercel. Single-file components where possible.
Design system

Background: #0a0a0a
Text primary: #e8e4dc
Text secondary: #555
Text muted: #2e2e2e
Accent green (live status): #22c55e
Borders: #1a1a1a to #1e1e1e
Feed background: #050505
Font headlines: Georgia, serif
Font labels/data/nav: monospace
Motion: subtle only — fade + 3–4px translateY on entry, nothing decorative

Component: Hero

Split-pane: grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr
Left: eyebrow label → h1 → bio → tool chips → stat strip (years exp, commits 30d, repos active)
Right: live GitHub feed via api.github.com/users/samhavasdesign/events/public
Feed polls every 60 seconds, pulses faintly green (#07100a) on new events
Graceful fallback to placeholder feed if API unavailable or rate-limited
For production: GitHub personal access token via NEXT_PUBLIC_GITHUB_TOKEN env variable

