Code rules

No localStorage or sessionStorage
No external UI libraries (no shadcn, no Radix unless explicitly requested)
No stock photography, no placeholder avatars
Keep all animations under 400ms
Every fetch wrapped in try/catch with graceful fallback
Relative timestamps on feed entries (e.g. "3m ago", "2d ago")
Feed rows: time | type tag | repo name + commit message

What not to do

No purple gradients
No Inter or Roboto
No generic Framer/Webflow template patterns
No decorative elements that don't serve a function
Don't add a skills section listing tools
Don't password-protect anything